Title: 'Love with freedom '
DateModified: '2019-02-21'
DatePublished: '2019-02-21'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/love-with-freedom
SetInCountry: Italy
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Yan Moura de carvalho
AuthorCountry: Italy
Text: this story tells of a copy of Italian boys in love, who are not accepted by
  their parents. one of them suffers from a serious illness that is not cured and
  therefore with little time to be together, so the two decide to travel throughout
  Europe in search of adventure. the last city that will stop will be portugal, where
  they will discover a new and more intense way of loving.
